review_text: Absolute beauty and peaceful surroundings.  Sunset is the most spectacular time of the day because the reflections off the water in addition to the ducks and Canada geese gracefully gliding and flying add to the tranquility this location has to offer.
It unfortunately has only one bench to sit. There are however big flat boulders available in place of benches to sit and watch the river and geese.

(Translated by Google) A small park with a bench to admire the beautiful view. Perfect for taking a walk and stopping at the park for a break.

(Original)
Un petit parc avec un banc pour admirer la belle vue. Parfait pour prendre une marche et arrêter au parc pour une pause.
